    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a vibrant red exterior and a muscular, aerodynamic body. The car features a long hood with dual air vents, a blacked-out front grille, and aggressive headlights. Its side profile reveals two doors, tinted windows, and prominent black alloy wheels with a multi-spoke design. The rear is equipped with a subtle black spoiler and wide taillights that span the width of the car. The roofline is smooth and slightly sloped, enhancing its sporty appearance. The overall design suggests high performance and modern styling, suitable for urban streets or high-speed driving.",
